{
  "id": "RAW_47e95c3c",
  "title": "曾拒绝在 Mac 植入广告！乔布斯坚守的“红线”，正被苹果一点点擦除",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247824887&idx=3&sn=936198da495299bfb5df7fb86e284c66",
  "date": "2025-11-10 10:43:00",
  "author": "CSDN",
  "siteName": "CSDN",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-category=\"正文\" data-mpa-template-id=\"1440\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">\n    <div>\n     <div style=\"padding:10px;text-decoration:inherit;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(240, 242, 246);font-family:inherit;border-style:solid;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;line-height:25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">【CSDN 编者按】乔布斯时代的苹果，以“极致的用户体验”闻名于世，也以那条不可逾越的“红线”守住了品牌灵魂。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，苹果昔日的信条似乎正在被现实稀释。本文从一位曾亲历乔布斯决策会议的业内人士视角出发，回顾那条红线的由来，审视苹果在库克时代的转向——从“体验优先”到“利润优先”，从信仰到生意，苹果的边界正悄然改变。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;line-height:25.6px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原文链接：<a href=\"https://kensegall.\" target=\"_blank\">https://kensegall.</a></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">com/2025/11/07/apple-is-crossing-a-steve-jobs-red-line</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">作者 | Ken Segall &nbsp; &nbsp; 翻译</span><span style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:1px;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;| 郑丽媛</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">出品 | CSDN（ID：CSDNnews）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要是说起</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">蒂姆·库克的毛病，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相信</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">倒出</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一箩筐</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而我认为</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最大</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的毛病</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就是</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他不是史蒂夫·乔布斯。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">乔布斯之所以</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">成为</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一名</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高效而富有远见的领导者，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">核心在于</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他的价值观极为清晰。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他能让苹果团队始终保持</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">着</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对“创新、设计与简洁”的信仰与执着。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但他还有一点几乎算是“老派”：</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他极度重视用户体验</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">乔布斯</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">看来，唯有创造最出色的体验，才能吸引新用户，并建立真正持久的品牌忠诚度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">回想</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上世纪 90 年代末，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">乔布斯回归那个濒临破产的苹果时，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就亲口在广告代理商的会议上给我们画下了蓝</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图——一切</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以用户体验</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从那一刻起，他愿意在提升体验的一切细节上“豪掷千金”，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时会毫不留情地拒绝</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">甚</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">至痛斥</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">任何会破坏</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">体验的</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">建议</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就是乔布斯的“红线”</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">谁敢越线，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">后果自负。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100341234\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"300\" style=\"width:214px;height:300px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fe844202&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq7kM1wTg0egO6WIh6oKvscdfrUGtmj3nvb2LDlQGibvKicFiaMNHCyvqJgLQnvX05p9wkqiblKsqCV0qSNkncicHyEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252192\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2c5b48b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QuwjkSP1G6wEJHaJCLTONqlcQexqRgJcIICxofIOJs6B6tWBfibb7now%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">这条红线，如今正在变得模糊</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而现在呢？这条红线似乎正在慢慢消失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最新消息称，Apple Maps（苹果地图）即将开始展示广告。就像 App Store 一样，先是在 2015 年出现广告位，然后在 2021 年进一步扩张。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不会</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有人</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">认为“被动看到广告”是一种更好的用户体验</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">那苹果为什么要这么做？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">答案</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很简单</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——钱。可以想象，苹果董事会听到这条“新收入来源”时，眼睛该有多亮。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">没人</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在乎</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些广告最终会被用户</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">接受。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，我们</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">已经</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生活在</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">了</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一个“到处都是广告”的时代</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但仍有不少人感到失望——这家全球最富有的公司</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">之一</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，竟也愿意为了</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">赚</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点“轻松的快钱”，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">出卖自己的一点灵魂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252191\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0d6be04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QDyP5HTUOXsPlJWd79yygiasaqXicpN7ibIfqiak5WFpaxE1mGxxpfmMjiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">“</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">那</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">乔布斯</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">会</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">怎么做？</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui,