纯粹、优雅、干净的界面体验。即便用户可以自由选择“带广告”或“不带广告”的版本，他仍然不愿让任何人看到这样被“污染”的系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">乔布斯明白，那才是苹果“王冠上的宝石”。他宁可放弃一点收入，也不愿牺牲体验的纯度</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他拒绝踏上那条“滑坡”，因为他知道——一旦踏上，就停不下来</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">了</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很好地</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">守住了</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">条红线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microso