m;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如今</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">苹果的演变告诉我们</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：红线不会永远存在。它能存活多久，完全取决于掌舵者是否愿意继续守护</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一旦没人维护，它就会慢慢模糊、甚至消失。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">无论出于何种理由，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">显然</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">蒂姆·库克不再像乔布斯那样执着于用户体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果我们现在去问他</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为什么在乔布斯时代不</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能做</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的事，如今却可以做？</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他大概会回答：“今天的苹果，已经不是当年的苹果。”这话</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">说得</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">没错——</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这，恰恰就是问题所在。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最后</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">总结一句：</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">乔布斯画下的那条“红线”，守的是信仰；库克擦掉的那条“红线”，换来的是利润</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">或许苹果依然伟大，但它已经不再纯粹。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
